text: "I Ain't Worried" is a 2022 song by American pop rock band OneRepublic and is the second and final single to the soundtrack for the movie Top Gun: Maverick. It topped the single charts in Belgium and New Zealand. It went to the top 10 in Australia, Austria, Brazil, Bulgaria, Canada, the Czech Republic, France, Greece, Hungary, Ireland, Lebanon, Lithuania, Malaysia, the Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Singapore, Slovakia, South Africa, South Korea, Switzerland, Taiwan, the United Kingdom and the United States.
